    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source of parts. The engine currently runs roughly and will require significant mechanical work to be roadworthy, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows several large dents, rust spots, and fading paint, while the interior has significant tearing and wear on the upholstery. It is being sold strictly 'as-is,' so please expect to invest time and resources into repairs.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
